description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Give your career a positive change.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Cygnet Health Care are proud to announce a new exciting opportunity for support workers to work in a brand new bespoke &amp; innovative community mental health Rehab service in Huddersfield. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Gledholt Mews &amp; Coach House focuses on rehabilitating people with mental health needs back into the community. You will be working with a multi-disciplinary clinical team with managing behavioural interventions and continuing practicing life skills and coping strategies. We are focused on developing community based activities, the use of public transport, education and vocational therapy, job placements, work experience and development of hobbies and interests.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Apply now to enjoy excellent career prospects while reaping the rewards of making a difference to others – every day&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;In this role you’ll:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work 42 hours per week (12 hour day shift and 13 hour night shift based on a rolling rota of 2 weeks of day shifts and 2 weeks of night shifts).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Offer enhanced care with a flexible learning approach for all our residents&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide guidance and encouragement to residents through physical and emotional support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain a safe, clean and enjoyable environment to live and work in&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assist residents with their medical and welfare needs and report as required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Safeguard residents&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn about individuals’ specific needs and provide help in the most appropriate way&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support with care planning and delivery of car&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;W&lt;strong&gt;e&#39;re looking for people who have:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and the ability to be a good team player&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion and drive to be different&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The sensitivity and energy required to provide a trusting, stimulating and varied lifestyle for the residents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to challenge themselves in order to create a service that makes a difference for the people we support and for all our team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A genuine desire to make a real difference in people’s lives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;In return we’ll offer you:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full training and Induction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid DBS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Group Pension&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS Staff Discounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhanced Maternity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Health Cash Plan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee Referral Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;24 Hours Free GP Helpline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discounted Gym Membership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cycle To Work Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On-site Benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Mortgage Broker &amp; Insurance Cover&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee Assistance Programme (EAP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Eye Tests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Car Lease Discounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid Life Assurance Company scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Smart Health Toolkit- Providing you with Fitness Programmes, Nutrition consultation and Health checks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;As part of our vibrant culture you’ll build lasting professional relationships that will take you further whatever your career goals.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Please note: &lt;/strong&gt;successful candidates will be required to undergo an enhanced DBS check.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
